data.title: Juniors
data.meta_description: The Florida State Golf Association provides Florida golfer; club, course, and tournament information, as well GHIN handicap, junior golf services, and much more.
data.text:
FJT Copperleaf

Wang & Lowry Conquer First FJT at Copperleaf

Xin Wang and Jamie Lowry each completed one-shot victories, their first in the 16-18 Division, at the first FJT event at Copperleaf Golf Club. Story | Results

FJT Sandridge

Drummond and Macapagal Start the Fall Strong

Nathan Drummond and Sofia Macapagal take home the first (13-15) FJT of the 2024 fall season. News Story | Results

Junior Florida Cup

South Team Three-Peats at Jr Fl Cup

The South team staged an epic comeback, beating the North team 17.5-14.5 securing three straight championship titles at the Junior Florida Cup. Recap | Full Results

Junior Amateur Match Play

Family Feat: Crowe Brothers Rule at Streamsong

Oscar and Henry Crowe capture the victory in the Boys (16-18) Division and Boys (13-15) Division respectively to dominate Junior Amateur Match Play. Results | Story

U.S. National Junior Team

Six Florida Juniors Make First-Ever National Team

The USGA announced the first U.S. National Junior Team. Out of the 18 players identified by the USGA (10 boys and 8 girls), six of them reside in Florida, three boys and three girls. Story | USGA Release
